{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a World Cup prediction widget section for a Shopify page with a dark premium streetwear aesthetic. Use EXACTLY the same layout structure as the Dutch version of this widget that was previously built for this store.
    
    LAYOUT STRUCTURE (must match exactly):
    - Full-width dark section, content centered in a max-width container
    - Top: contest header text, left-aligned or centered
    - Below header: countdown timer with 4 boxes side by side (Days | Hours | Minutes | Seconds), each box has a large number and a small label underneath, gold border or accent
    - Below timer: gold scarcity badge/pill
    - Below badge: the form (email field full width, then two score inputs side by side with team labels above them, then goalscorers text field full width, then full-width gold submit button)
    - Below form: success message (hidden until submit)
    - Below form: prizes section with two rows of prize text with emoji icons
    - All elements left-aligned within the container, generous padding
    
    DESIGN:
    - Dark background #000000, white text, gold accent #c9a84c
    - Minimal, editorial typography (clean sans-serif)
    - Form inputs: dark background, subtle border, white text
    - Submit button: gold background (#c9a84c), black text, full width
    - Countdown boxes: dark with gold accent border or background highlight on the number
    
    CONTENT (ALL TEXT IN ENGLISH):
    - Header: "Morocco vs Brazil — June 14, 2026"
    - Live countdown timer to June 14 2026 00:10 CEST (June 13 2026 22:10 UTC) — boxes labeled "Days", "Hours", "Minutes", "Seconds"
    - After deadline show "Submissions are closed." and hide the form
    - Scarcity badge: "~18 shirts remaining" in gold
    - Form fields:
      - Email (required, label: "Your email address")
      - Two side-by-side number inputs labeled "Morocco" and "Brazil" (min 0, integers only)
      - Optional text field: "Goalscorers (optional)" with placeholder "e.g. Hakimi, En-Nesyri, Vinicius — comma-separated"
      - Submit button: "Enter now"
    - Success message: "Your prediction has been saved! We'll let you know if you've won."
    - Prizes:
      - "🎯 Correct score → €15 discount"
      - "🏆 Correct score + goalscorer → Free shirt"
    
    FUNCTIONALITY:
    - Deadline: June 14 2026 00:10 CEST = June 13 2026 22:10:00 UTC
    - After deadline: hide form, show "Submissions are closed."
    - On submit: save customer with email via Shopify API, add tags "wk-voorspelling" and "mar-bra-2026", store prediction in customer note or metafield
    - DUPLICATE CHECK: only show "You've already entered!" if the email has ALREADY submitted a prediction for this contest (has tag mar-bra-2026 AND stored prediction). Do NOT block existing customers who have not yet submitted.
    - All text in English
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-wc-widget-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 20px;
  }

  .ai-wc-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-wc-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.header_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.spacing }}px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_align }};
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .ai-wc-countdown-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.countdown_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.spacing }}px;
    {% if block.settings.text_align == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-wc-countdown-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.box_padding }}px;
    border: {{ block.settings.box_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.box_border_radius }}px;
    min-width: {{ block.settings.box_min_width }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.box_background }};
  }

  .ai-wc-countdown-number-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.countdown_number_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ai-wc-countdown-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.countdown_label_size }}px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .ai-wc-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.badge_padding_v }}px {{ block.settings.badge_padding_h }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.badge_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.badge_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.spacing }}px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .ai-wc-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.form_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-wc-input-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-wc-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.input_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.input_background }};
    border: {{ block.settings.input_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_font_size }}px;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ai-wc-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}::placeholder,
  .ai-wc-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}::placeholder {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .ai-wc-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus,
  .ai-wc-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
  }

  .ai-wc-score-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.form_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-wc-score-field-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-wc-team-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .ai-wc-submit-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-wc-submit-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ai-wc-submit-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-wc-message-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.input_padding }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_font_size }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.spacing }}px;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-wc-message-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-wc-success-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: rgba(21, 170, 11, 0.1);
    color: #15aa0b;
    border: 1px solid #15aa0b;
  }

  .ai-wc-error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: rgba(255, 109, 109, 0.1);
    color: #ff6d6d;
    border: 1px solid #ff6d6d;
  }

  .ai-wc-closed-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_font_size }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.input_padding }}px;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.7;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-wc-closed-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-wc-prizes-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.prize_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-wc-prize-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.prize_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-wc-countdown-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: {{ block.settings.countdown_gap | times: 0.6 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-wc-countdown-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.box_padding | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
      min-width: {{ block.settings.box_min_width | times: 0.8 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-wc-countdown-number-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.countdown_number_size | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-wc-countdown-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.countdown_label_size | times: 0.85 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-wc-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
